<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,758,1430]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,401,758,783]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">Original description.</emphasis>
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">
&quot; 
<taxonomicName box="[419,584,758,782]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longirostris">L. longirostris</taxonomicName>
, niger, elytris striatis acutis flavo pulverulentis. Lixo paraplectico major et crassior. Antennae tenues, nigrae. Rostrum cylindricum, thorace longius, nigrum. Thorax rugosus, niger, immaculatus. Elytra vix punctato-striata, flavo pulverulenta, apice acuto reflexo. Pedes flavo pubescentes femoribus muticis&quot;.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
